  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if using school-based telemedicine for diabetes
      support and education in students with type 1 diabetes in grades K-8 can lead to improvement
      in control of diabetes and improved satisfaction of all caregivers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
